name: Dino's Egg Hunt
description:
This video game is part of a youtube video I made. The joke was that I could make a better Dino Jump Game than google. I added a innovative game mechanic which will change the way how game developer makes games. Jokes aside, this is the first video game I have ever made and I just wanted to create a funny video.
